OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FEarly showery rain and
OL,6,Fthunderstorms gradually clearing
OL,7,Fnorthwards, with bright or sunny
OL,8,Fspells following. Further scattered
OL,9,Fthunderstorms developing in the
OL,10,Fafternoon, with the risk of some
OL,11,Flocally heavy downpours, hail,
OL,12,Ffrequent lightning and gusty winds.
OL,13,FFeeling very warm and humid.
OL,14,
OL,15,CTonight:FEvening showers and
OL,16,Fthunderstorms gradually fading to
OL,17,Fleave a largely dry night, with some
OL,18,Flengthy clear spells. Still a warm and
OL,19,Fhumid night for many.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
