OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FLargely dry with variable
OL,6,Famounts of cloud and bright or sunny
OL,7,Fspells. Perhaps some outbreaks of rain
OL,8,Freaching western hills late in the
OL,9,Fday. Breezier and feeling a little
OL,10,Ffresher.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FEarly
OL,13,Frain clearing to brighter and fresher
OL,14,Fconditions with scattered showers
OL,15,FSunday. Breezy with sunny spells and
OL,16,Fscattered showers Monday. Further
OL,17,Fscattered showers Tuesday. Feeling
OL,18,Fmuch fresher than of late.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
